        "body": "Issue: closes https://github.com/simple-icons/simple-icons/issues/14039\r\n\r\nPopularity Metric:\r\nThe Ona website (https://ona.com) has a Traffic.cv global rank of 240,795, meeting the popularity requirement.\r\n\r\nTerms of Service link:\r\nOna is a rebrand of Gitpod, an open source platform, and publicly provides brand assets without restriction. No additional permission is required.\r\n\r\nChecklist\r\n- [x] I have reviewed the forbidden brands list and confirm the brand I am submitting a PR for is not one of them, nor is it a subsidiary of one of those brands.\r\n- [x] I have reviewed the brand's terms of service, and am confident we can add this icon.\r\n- [x] I updated the JSON data in `data/simple-icons.json`\r\n- [x] I optimized the icon with SVGO or SVGOMG\r\n- [x] The SVG viewBox is `0 0 24 24`\r\n\r\nDescription\r\nThe hex color `#E05939` represents the official primary brand color from Ona.\r\nThe icon SVG was sourced from the official Ona favicon assets:\r\nhttps://ona.com/ona-dark-favicon.svg\r\n\r\nMinor optimizations with SVGO were performed to comply with Simple Icons formatting requirements.\r\nThis pull request adds support for the Ona brand and is tied to the rebranding from Gitpod, noted publicly:\r\nhttps://ona.com/stories/gitpod-is-now-ona\r\n",
